nodes.text: Mos Taike was a settlement built on the edge of the Northern Dune Sea, on the desert planet Tatooine.

Mos Taike was first mentioned in the Star Wars Legends reference book Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Episode I, which was written by Kristin Lund and released on October 1, 2001. The settlement was first mentioned in canon when elements from Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Episode I were rereleased as part of the reference book Star Wars: Complete Locations on September 27, 2016.
